00:06:21.810 --> 00:06:25.530
And it's a crowd scene and, of
course, there are soldiers in it.

00:06:25.530 --> 00:06:29.260
And right at the center
are two nuns.

00:06:29.260 --> 00:06:35.290
And it really brought home to
me how much they were there

00:06:35.290 --> 00:06:39.740
and how they have been
somewhat erased from our memory.

00:06:39.740 --> 00:06:44.440
So there was also that
incentive to bring them back

00:06:44.440 --> 00:06:48.100
