00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:17.960
And something I found really
fascinating about this novel,

00:09:17.960 --> 00:09:20.130
it begins with a suicide.

00:09:20.130 --> 00:09:23.790
There's a love affair, which
is very much part of the plot.

00:09:23.790 --> 00:09:27.980
And there's somebody who suffers
from depression, we learn later on.

00:09:27.980 --> 00:09:30.670
And I thought to myself
these are three things

00:09:30.670 --> 00:09:34.610
that so many contemporary novels
are completely built around

00:09:34.610 --> 00:09:38.540
and we learn everything you need to
know about suicide, love affairs,

00:09:38.540 --> 00:09:40.760
and depression they
could possibly know.

00:09:40.760 --> 00:09:45.210
And yet in this book, as
important as they are to the novel,

00:09:45.210 --> 00:09:47.990
you tell us very little about,

00:09:47.990 --> 00:09:50.680
really they never talk
about the suicide.

00:09:50.680 --> 00:09:54.550 position:56%
Once we know the affair is underway,
